<https://w3id.org/beast/ontology#isTextualReferenceOf> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://w3id.org/beast/ontology#isTextualReferenceOf> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf> <https://w3id.org/beast/ontology#hasTextualReference> .
