# https://w3id.org/beast/ontology#Omnivorous
<https://w3id.org/beast/ontology#Omnivorous> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://w3id.org/beast/ontology#Omnivorous> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://w3id.org/beast/ontology#Diet> .
<https://w3id.org/beast/ontology#Omnivorous> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A diet consisting of both animal and plant matter."@en .
<https://w3id.org/beast/ontology#Omnivorous> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/beast/ontology#BiologicalModule> .
<https://w3id.org/beast/ontology#Omnivorous> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Omnivorous"@en .
