<https://w3id.org/beast/ontology#ScientificTaxonomy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A genre focused on the scientific categorization and biological documentation of animals (e.g. Aldrovandi and Paré)."@en .
<https://w3id.org/beast/ontology#ScientificTaxonomy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://w3id.org/beast/ontology#ProvenanceModule> .
